Nigerian singer, Folarin Falana, popularly known as Falz, has revealed that he has never fallen in love with a woman throughout his entire life. The singer disclosed this while speaking in a interview with the host Tea wit Taypod, Temisan Emmanuel, expressing that he has never said the three special words, ‘I love you’ to a girl. He said, “I have not been in love before sha, I have never been in love. “I have never said to a woman in a romantical way, ‘I am in love with you’. I have never done that. I have never said ‘I love you’ to a girl.”